l":"https://www.backflipt.com/"}}]}</script><section class="md:py-16 pt-28 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative w-full"><div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-2"><div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 items-center justify-center gap-8"><div class="text-left max-w-6xl"><h1 class="text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2  leading-[60px]">Discover. Trust. Govern. Observe. </h1><h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2  leading-[50px]">Zero-Trust Control for A2A Agent-to-Agent AI Collaboration</h2><div class="flex gap-4 mt-4" id="button"><a target="_blank" class="inline-flex justify-center items-center px-4 py-2 font-medium text-white bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-800 to-sky-500 hover:bg-gradient-to-r  hover:from-sky-600 hover:to-blue-600 rounded-lg focus:ring-4 focus:ring-blue-300" href="https://calendly.com/backflipt/schedule-a-meeting-with-us?month=2025-11"><svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white mr-2" aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 10h16m-8-3V4M7 7V4m10 3V4M5 20h14a1 1 0 0 0 1-1V7a1 1 0 0 0-1-1H5a1 1 0 0 0-1 1v12a1 1 0 0 0 1 1Zm3-7h.01v.01H8V13Zm4 0h.01v.01H12V13Zm4 0h.01v.01H16V13Zm-8 4h.01v.01H8V17Zm4 0h.01v.01H12V17Zm4 0h.01v.01H16V17Z"></path></svg><span>Schedule Meeting</span></a></div></div><div class="justify-start md:justify-end flex"><img alt="Drive Enterprise transformation with Agentic AI-powered applications" fetchPriority="high" width="200" height="120" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="w-full md:w-[80%] md:mx-0 py-10 pb-10" style="color:transparent" src="/images/common/homepage_14.svg"/></div></div><a class="md:absolute bottom-2 text-lg right-0 text-sky-600 underline" href="/managed-file-transfer-products"><span>Click here for Managed File Transfer Products  →</span></a></div></section><section class="  relative py-16 bg-white"><div class="px-4 mx-auto max-w-screen-xl"><div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 justify-center items-center"><div class=""><h2 class="text-2xl text-gray-800 font-bold mb-3">Secure Agent-to-Agent Collaboration with Lumen A2A Gateway</h2><p>The Lumen A2A Gateway delivers centralized zero-trust governance, unifying security, privacy, business policies, and operational controls, enforcing them in real time across all agent-to-agent interactions in regulated enterprises deploying autonomous AI agents.<br/>In finance, healthcare, and insurance, regulated enterprises use autonomous AI agents to automate complex workflows.<br/><br/>The Lumen A2A Gateway gives IT administrators centralized control over these interactions, blocking unauthorized actions, enforcing thresholds, requiring approvals, mitigating cascading vulnerabilities, and maintaining compliance..</p><h3 class="font-bold mt-3">Key Benefits</h3><ul class="space-y-3 mt-2 text-left"><li class="flex space-x-3 items-baseline"><svg class="shrink-0 w-3.5 h-3.5 text-blue-500 dark:text-blue-400" aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 16 12"><path stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M1 5.917 5.724 10.5 15 1.5"></path></svg><span>Securely connect autonomous AI agents across platforms, including Salesforce, ServiceNow, AWS, Azure, and Google Cloud.​</span></li><li class="items-baseline"><p class="flex space-x-3 "><svg class="shrink-0 w-3.5 h-3.5 text-blue-500 dark:text-blue-400" aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 16 12"><path stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M1 5.917 5.724 10.5 15 1.5"></path></svg><span>Empower IT administrators with centralized policy management across security, compliance &amp; privacy, business policy &amp; risk, and operational assurance—using global rules with agent-specific overrides.​</span></p></li><li class="flex space-x-3 items-baseline"><svg class="shrink-0 w-3.5 h-3.5 text-blue-500 dark:text-blue-400" aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 16 12"><path stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M1 5.917 5.724 10.5 15 1.5"></path></svg><span>Deliver granular control over interactions, including READ/WRITE/OFF-LIMITS permissions, transaction thresholds, approval workflows, action prohibitions, rate limiting, and anomaly detection.​ </span></li><li class="flex space-x-3 items-baseline"><svg class="shrink-0 w-3.5 h-3.5 text-blue-500 dark:text-blue-400" aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 16 12"><path stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M1 5.917 5.724 10.5 15 1.5"></path></svg><span>Enforce policies in real time with immutable logging.​ </span></li></ul></div><div class=" justify-end items-end flex flex-col w-full gap-8"><img alt="Luman " loading="lazy" width="80" height="80" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="w-full md:w-[70%] rounded-md" style="color:transparent" src="/images/common/lumen-gateway.svg"/></div></div><div class="grid mt-6 sm:grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4"><div class="p-6 rounded-md flex flex-col justify-center items-center bg-white  transition-transform  duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 border border-gray-200 shadow-md"><img alt="flow" loading="lazy" width="80" height="80" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="" style="color:transparent" src="/images/partners-icon.png"/><h4 class="text-xl text-gray-800 font-bold my-3">Discover &amp; Trust</h4><p>Auto-identify agents and register with zero-trust identities — securing every interaction from the start.</p></div><div class="p-6 rounded-md flex flex-col justify-center items-center bg-white transition-transform duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 border border-gray-200 shadow-md"><img alt="flow" loading="lazy" width="80" height="80" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="" style="color:transparent" src="/images/common/lumen-home-3.png"/><h4 class="text-xl text-gray-800 font-bold my-3">Govern</h4><p>Enforce consistent policies across all agent conversations for security, compliance, and cost control.</p></div><div class="p-6 rounded-md flex flex-col justify-center items-center bg-white  transition-transform duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 border border-gray-200 shadow-md"><img alt="flow" loading="lazy" width="80" height="80" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="mb-2" style="color:transparent" src="/images/common/lumen-home-1.png"/><h4 class="text-xl text-gray-800 font-bold my-3">Observe</h4><p>Log and visualize every agent-to-agent exchange for full transparency and rapid issue resolution.</p></div></div></div></section><section class="py-16 relative bg-gray-100"><div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-4"><div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 justify-center items-center"><div class="text-left"><h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-3 text-gray-900">Deployment and Integration</h2><p class="mt-4">The Lumen A2A Gateway deploys as a Dockerized container, with native Kubernetes support for horizontal scaling and high availability. It runs in environments such as AWS, Azure, GCP, on-premises data centers, or air- gapped setups. This deployment model keeps all data processing and storage under customer control, with no external egress.<br/><br/>Deployed alongside leading AI security solutions, the Lumen A2A Gateway complements their core features, providing specialized governance for agent- to-agent interactions.</p></div><div class="flex md:justify-end justify-center "><img alt="lumen_logo" loading="lazy" width="100" height="100" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="w-[70%] flex md:justify-end justify-center md:items-end items-center" style="color:transparent" src="/images/common/lumen-a2a-works.png"/></div></div></div></section><section class=" py-16 relative px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 bg-white"><div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-5"><div class=""><div class="text-center"><h2 class="mb-3 text-3xl font-bold">Agent Platform Compatibility</h2><p class="">Lumen Gateway works alongside agents from leading platforms with no forklift upgrades required. Gain visibility and control over agents in AWS, Azure, GCP, Salesforce, ServiceNow, Snowflake, and many others — all through a single vendor-agnostic solution.</p></div><div class="grid mt-6 sm:grid-cols-3 md:grid-cols-5 lg:grid-cols-7 gap-4 text-center"><div class="p-2 rounded-md flex flex-col justify-center items-center border transition-transform border-gray-300 duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2"><img alt="flow" loading="lazy" width="70" height="70" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="w-[30px]" style="color:transparent" src="/images/common/landing-1.png"/><p>AWS AgentCore</p></div><div class="p-2 rounded-md flex flex-col justify-center items-center border transition-transform border-gray-300 duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 "><img alt="flow" loading="lazy" width="70" height="70" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="w-[30px]" style="color:transparent" src="/images/common/lumen-afa-6.png"/><p>Azure AI</p></div><div class="p-2 rounded-md flex flex-col justify-center items-center border transition-transform border-gray-300 duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2"><img alt="flow" loading="lazy" width="70" height="70" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="w-[30px]" style="color:transparent" src="/images/common/landing-2.png"/><p>Google Cloud Vertex</p></div><div class="p-2 rounded-md flex flex-col justify-center items-center border transition-transform border-gray-300 duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2"><img alt="flow" loading="lazy" width="70" height="70" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="w-[30px]" style="color:transparent" src="/images/common/landing-3.png"/><p>Salesforce Agentforce</p></div><div class="p-2 rounded-md flex flex-col justify-center items-center border transition-transform border-gray-300 duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 "><img alt="flow" loading="lazy" width="70" height="70" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="w-[30px]" style="color:transparent" src="/images/common/landing-4.png"/><p>ServiceNow AI Agents</p></div><div class="p-2 rounded-md flex flex-col justify-center items-center  border transition-transform border-gray-300 duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2"><img alt="flow" loading="lazy" width="70" height="70" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="w-[30px]" style="color:transparent" src="/images/common/landing-5.png"/><p>Snowflake Cortex</p></div><div class="p-2 rounded-md flex flex-col justify-center items-center  border transition-transform border-gray-300 duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2"><img alt="flow" loading="lazy" width="70" height="70" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="w-[30px]" style="color:transparent" src="/images/common/landing-6.png"/><p>And others</p></div></div></div></div></section><section class="relative bg-gray-100 py-16 px-4 border-t border-b border-blue-200"><div class="px-4 mx-auto max-w-screen-xl"><div class="md:mb-3 text-3xl font-bold text-center"><span class=" block">Latest from the Blog</span></div><div class="grid mt-6 md:grid-cols-1 gap-4 text-center"><div class="text-left"><h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">AWS Transfer Family</h2><h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mt-4">From sprawl to strategy</h3><p class="text-[#263238] my-3">How TransferIQ Orchestrate enforces zero-trust controls, audit readiness, and continuous compliance across AWS Transfer Family environments</p><a class="mb-2 md:mb-0  flex font-medium text-sky-600  mr-2" href="https://backflipt.com/blogs/from-sprawl-to-strategy/"><span>Read the blog →</span></a></div></div></div></section><section class="  relative py-16 bg-white"><div class="px-4 mx-auto max-w-screen-xl"><div class="flex flex-col md:justify-center md:items-center"><h2 class="md:mb-3 text-3xl font-bold">Lumen AI Products</h2></div><div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 py-4 md:py-10 justify-center items-center"><div class=""><h2 class="text-2xl text-gray-800 font-bold mb-3">Lumen A2A Gateway</h2><p>The Lumen A2A Gateway delivers centralized zero-trust governance for autonomous AI agents across multi-platform environments. It discovers and registers agents from leading platforms, including Salesforce AgentForce, ServiceNow AI Agents, Amazon Bedrock Agents, Microsoft Azure AI Agents, Google Cloud Vertex AI Agents, and Snowflake Cortex. It enforces uniform policies in real time and provides full observability through detailed logging.<br/><br/>Eliminating risks from uncontrolled agent-to-agent interactions, including unauthorized actions, threshold breaches, cascading vulnerabilities, and violations of HIPAA, GDPR, SOC 2, and the EU AI Act.</p></div><div class=" justify-end items-end flex flex-col w-full gap-8"><img alt="Luman " loading="lazy" width="80" height="80" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="w-full md:w-[70%] rounded-md" style="color:transparent" src="/images/common/lumen-gateway.svg"/></div></div><div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 py-10 justify-center border-t border-b border-gray-200 items-center"><div class="justify-center flex flex-col w-full gap-8 order-2 md:order-1"><img alt="Luman " loading="lazy" width="80" height="80" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="w-full md:w-[90%] rounded-md" style="color:transparent" src="/images/common/lumen-poet-agent.svg"/></div><div class="order-1 md:order-2"><h2 class="text-2xl text-gray-800 font-bold my-3">Lumen POET: API to AI Agents</h2><p>Lumen POET automatically transforms APIs from your gateways into fully functional AI agents. Lumen POET auto-generates optimized prompts, instantly converts APIs into capable agents, and enables product owners to add tools and features through an intuitive interface. No AI expertise is required.<br/><br/>Lumen POET lets products quickly gain AI interfaces without scarce specialists and slashes time-to-market. Organizations join the agent-to-agent economy securely, with agents interacting across systems. POET provides CISO-level governance via immutable audit logs and real-time insights and runs on any hyperscaler cloud (AWS, Azure, GCP) or air-gapped infrastructure. Total data control is ensured.</p></div></div><div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 pt-10 gap-8 justify-center items-center"><div class=""><h2 class="text-2xl text-gray-800 font-bold mb-3">Lumen AI TransferView: AI-Powered Visibility for Governed File Transfers (formerly Lumen FileView)</h2><p>Powered by Galileo, built-in agentic AI companion from the Lumen family, Lumen AI TransferView, ingests logs from leading managed file transfer (MFT) platforms. It supports natural-language queries to instantly locate files, analyze transfer patterns, and uncover insights. Galileo auto-generates personalized dashboards, reports, and SLA monitoring rules, while proactively detecting issues.<br/><br/>This delivers real-time governance of sensitive partner data within the Lumen suite. Teams can detect breaches instantly, automate notifications (email, Teams, Slack), create incident tickets (e.g., ServiceNow), and resolve issues without manual effort or expertise.<br/><br/>Organizations gain proactive risk mitigation, full regulatory compliance, role-based access with SAML SSO, and quick deployment as a Docker container in any cloud (AWS, Azure, GCP) or on-premises—ensuring data sovereignty and seamless operations.</p></div><div class=" justify-end items-end flex flex-col w-full gap-8"><img alt="Luman " loading="lazy" width="80" height="80" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="w-full md:w-[85%] rounded-md" style="color:transparent" src="/images/common/lumen-ai-transferview.svg"/></div></div></div></section><section class="relative bg-banner py-16 border-t border-b border-blue-200 flex"><div class="px-4 mx-auto max-w-screen-xl"><div class="text-center"><div class="text-3xl font-bold">Whitepaper</div><h3 class="mt-2 text-xl font-bold">Governing Autonomous AI Agents in the Enterprise </h3><p class="text-[#263238] mt-3">Empowering IT and CSO Teams with Centralized Control in a Multi-Agent World</p><div class="flex items-center justify-center mt-4"><a target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="mb-2 md:mb-0 inline-flex px-4 py-2 mt-0 font-medium text-sky-600 border-2 border-sky-600 rounded-lg" href="https://243452294.fs1.hubspotusercontent-na2.net/hubfs/243452294/White%20Papers/Lumen/Centralized%20Control%20for%20a%20Multi-Agent%20World.pdf"><img alt="flow" loading="lazy" width="18" height="18" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="mr-2" style="color:transparent" src="/images/common/pdf.svg"/>Download Now</a><a target="_blank" class="inline-flex justify-center items-center px-4 py-2 ml-3 font-medium text-white bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-800 to-sky-500 hover:bg-gradient-to-r border-2 border-sky-600 hover:from-sky-600 hover:to-blue-600 rounded-lg focus:ring-4 focus:ring-blue-300" href="https://calendly.com/backflipt/schedule-a-meeting-with-us?month=2025-11"><svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white mr-2" aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 10h16m-8-3V4M7 7V4m10 3V4M5 20h14a1 1 0 0 0 1-1V7a1 1 0 0 0-1-1H5a1 1 0 0 0-1 1v12a1 1 0 0 0 1 1Zm3-7h.01v.01H8V13Zm4 0h.01v.01H12V13Zm4 0h.01v.01H16V13Zm-8 4h.01v.01H8V17Zm4 0h.01v.01H12V17Zm4 0h.01v.01H16V17Z"></path></svg><span>Schedule Meeting</span></a></div></div></div></section><!--$--><!--/$--><footer class="bg-linear-to-r footer-bg relative overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-t border-t border-gray-200 from-blue-50 to-gray-100"><div class="mx-auto w-full max-w-screen-xl"><div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 px-4 pt-6 pb-6 md:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-4"><div class="relative"><h2 class="mb-3 mt-8 text-sm font-semibold text-gray-800 uppercase">Products</h2><ul class="font-medium text-gray-700 "><li class="mb-3"><a class="hover:underline" href="/lumen-a2a-gateway">Lumen A2A Gateway</a></li><li class="mb-3"><a class="hover:under